author: jm
msg: add spamc '-z' switch, which compresses mails to be scanned using zlib compression; very useful for long-distance use of spamc over the internet.  also add test script, INSTALL doc, and documentation.  backport from r481882 on 'jm_spamc_hacks' branch

author: kpvdr
msg: Fixed: [QPID-253] Existing classpath breaks codegen; [QPID-254] Build failure does not prevent timestamp from being generated. Also moved all required properties into ant build file, allowing the generation to be completed independently of Maven from the common directory.
